<p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">6月13日，我校党委副书记、执行校长范红铭，副校长郭宏、副校长傅志军、副校长吴志勇等一行13人赴湖南软件职业技术大学交流，该校执行校长杨虹、副校长刘上冰、副校长陈晓慧等热情接待。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-06-23%2017%3A18%3A17%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240623171808.jpg?Expires=2034494298&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=%2BymP%2Bkuj2aLX3R5eJND9xcibFCs%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">范红铭一行实地考察了该校校史馆、湘潭市数字经济孵化基地和潇湘电影数字创意产业学院等地，对该校办学特色、办学成就以及校企合作人才培养模式给予了高度评价。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-06-23%2017%3A19%3A01%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240623171856.jpg?Expires=2034494341&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=J0%2FeedCpUzwqUOitFBryODXHsBk%3D" alt="" width="650" height="384" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">在图书馆五楼会议室召开的座谈会上，杨虹对范红铭率团交流表示热烈欢迎，并热情介绍了学校办学历史、办学特色、校企合作、学生管理、职业本科建设等方面的情况。双方进行了多方面深入交流，并在学校品牌建设、人才培养、专业建设等方面达成共识。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">湖南软件职业技术大学教学质量监控与评估中心副主任李惠、人事处副处长李晓霞、学工处副处长胡斯逸分别围绕本科人才培养，师资队伍建设和学生教育管理等方面介绍了学校建设发展的情况。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">范红铭表示，江西软件职业技术大学与湖南软件职业技术大学作为兄弟院校在办学方向、办学理念上有许多相似之处，希望双方以此次调研交流为契机，建立长效沟通机制，拓宽合作领域。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">我校党政办主任陶磊、教务处处长李嵩、学工部（处）部长邱忠镇、网络工程学院党总支书记曾继勇、人事处副处长周洪波、招就处副处长龚倩、评建办顾问何习平等，湖南软件职业技术大学党宣传部、校办公室、校企合作办、招生就业处、人事处、学工处、教学质量监控与评估中心等部门负责人参加了座谈。</span></p><p><br/></p>